content:
Install Insurance for the first time.

Do not install the Insurance managed package if the OmniStudio managed package is already installed. Having both packages installed results in duplicate components.

If your org already has the OmniStudio package installed and you want to install Insurance, contact Salesforce support for help.

To complete the installation:

Complete Pre-Install Tasks
Install Packages:
Managed Packages
Unmanaged Packages
Vlocity Installation Assistant

Find the most recent package links in the Insurance Release Summary.

Complete Vlocity Installation Assistant Steps
Complete Post-Installation Tasks
Package Installation Flows

You need to perform a few additional steps to complete your installation, including setting up user access with Insurance permission sets and building Insurance product models.
title: Installing Salesforce Insurance
